sources.description:
Kidnapped brides horror... to make your hair stand on end! Thrills... to make you grip the edge of your seat! See... a secret of love... sealed by death!
A scientist, aided by an old hag and her two sons, kills virginal brides, steals their bodies, and extracts gland fluid to keep his ancient wife alive and young.

Original title: The Corpse Vanishes (1942) AKA The Case of the Missing Brides


Colorized version https://youtu.be/dSBchGJzCJY

Director: Wallace Fox
Writers: Sam Robins, Gerald Schnitzer, Harvey Gates
Stars: Bela Lugosi, Luana Walters, Tristram Coffin 
Genres: Classics, Cult Film, Horror, Sci-Fi
